  "title": "Program Engineer (Mechanical drawing/Quotation, Woodlands)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Woodlands</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Mon to Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Salary up $3000-$4800</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Have AWS &amp; bonus</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review quote requests in detail and ensure all quotes for Module line are provided within the set Lead time</li>\n  <li>Follow up with manufacturing for New Product Introduction and ensure they are manufactured as per spec and delivered on time.</li>\n  <li>Follow up with Manufacturing and ensure effective implementation.</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with Planners and ensure material is received on time for new products</li>\n  <li>Develop, evaluate, and improve manufacturing methods continuously</li>\n  <li>Involve in Failure analysis for any customer returns</li>\n  <li>Drives suppliers for cost reduction along with SCM team</li>\n  <li>Perform other duties as requested by managemen</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s degree / Post Graduate Diploma in Industrial / Mechanical / Mechatronic / Electromechanical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years relevant working experience</li>\n  <li>Able to prepare quotation</li>\n  <li>Able to read mechanical drawing</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified*</strong></u></p>\n<p>Please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong></p>\n<p>Alternatively, you may also email your resume to us at <a href=\"mailto:emily.fong@atomrecruit.com\"><strong>emily.fong@atomrecruit.com</strong></a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Emily Fong</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Senior Talent Specialist</strong></p>\n<p>Atomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443<br>\nEA Personnel Reg No.: R1768368</p>",
